snippet.title: Seclusion Islesbury Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Seclusion Islesbury is a horror adventure game that creates a dark and cold world for you to explore and interact with. Can you uncover the mysterious of this inhospitable town?

Follow us for more at:
http://silentgamehouse.com/
http://twitter.com/SilentGameHouse
http://www.facebook.com/SeclusionIslesbury
http://www.indiedb.com/games/seclusion-islesbury

Song: 
You Yourself and the Main Character by Komiku 
https://chezmonplaisir.bandcamp.com/
